{"tid":1128568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環鬧市男子遭拮傷屁股　警當場拘持刀漢","createTime":"2019-04-28T01:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T02:50:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cb41e81a2b4bcd9af72c9f23260bf43e985b7c55","tid":1128568,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190427/photo/bkn-20190427234058529-0427_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190428002825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190427234058529-0427_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190428002825&h=bf86cd96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日（27日）下午2時許，一名姓梁（38歲）男子，在港鐵中環站近戲院里出口，突遭一名姓楊（25歲）男子用一把約9厘米長摺刀襲擊，臀部被刺中受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報迅速到場，當場將楊拘捕，以涉嫌傷人扣查。梁由救護員送院治理，他報稱不知遇襲原因，中區警區刑事調查隊正跟進調查傷人動機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190427/bkn-20190427234058529-0427_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190427%2Fbkn-20190427234058529-0427_00822_001.html&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8nwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=bc275e87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190427/bkn-20190427234058529-0427_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"befc5591b8d3ed7b2ebcae515b9ca2cbb0bf0e2c","tid":1128568,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"拮c眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4a88e1e5cfac30141c1abf76cdbd852ed85d59","tid":1128568,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T02:01:28.000Z","msg":"咁似cctvb一套之前既電視劇情節既"},{"pid":"665101e68f037265e12f0afcf14e96d65863a1bd","tid":1128568,"uid":113373,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T02:01:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請大家出嚟 唔好放棄香港</span><br />\n<br />\n